>> time required: 1 hours
>> course: sauce

Deed seed about half of @habenero peppers{20-25}
Roughly chop @sweet onion{.5}, @garlic cloves{3} and fry in @olive oil{1.5%tbsp} until translucent
Add peppers, @white vinegar{1%cup}, @sugar{3%tbsp}, and @salt{1%tsp}
Bring to boil and simmer for a few minutes
Blend in blender
Optional add @xanthan gum{1%pinch} to stabilize.
